  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK669">
<l>tuṉpa muṟavariṉuñ ceyka tuṇivāṟṟi </l>
<l>yiṉpam payakkum viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though it should cause increasing sorrow (at the outset), do with firmness the act that yield bliss (in the end).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
